        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13068#issuecomment-4237356602\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/13068\">issue #13068</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>er, sorry, the test case here is <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/alexcrichton/7fe97b9ede4da45ac25e80609b84303d\">this one</a> (fuzz-generated)</p>\n</blockquote>",
